      <title>孟加拉国被罢免的领导人谢赫·哈西娜之子称其不会再回来</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/bangladesh-s-ousted-leader-sheikh-hasina-won-t-return-son-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[谢赫·哈西娜在针对其统治的激烈抗议中于本周辞去总理职务并逃离孟加拉国，她不打算返回这个由她的家人共同打造的国家。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/bangladesh-s-ousted-leader-sheikh-hasina-won-t-return-son-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 08:10:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯与乌克兰边境交战，死亡人数上升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/death-toll-rises-as-russia-battles-border-incursion-from-ukraine</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯库尔斯克地区的战斗进入第二天，莫斯科官员称数百名乌克兰士兵入侵，使总统弗拉基米尔·普京的入侵再次回到了自己的领土。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/death-toll-rises-as-russia-battles-border-incursion-from-ukraine</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 07:55:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>意大利或将提高富人的海外所得税：Messaggero</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/italy-may-raise-foreign-income-tax-for-wealthy-messaggero-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[意大利可能会提高对新居民外国收入的统一税率，这将使该国成为全球富人的首选目的地。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/italy-may-raise-foreign-income-tax-for-wealthy-messaggero-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 07:08:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>据《时代》报道，Rachel Reeves 计划成立“加拿大式”养老基金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/rachel-reeves-plans-canada-style-pension-funds-times-reports</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据《泰晤士报》报道，英国政府正考虑合并多个地方政府养老金计划，汇集其 3600 亿英镑（4580 亿美元）的资产，并创建“加拿大模式”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/rachel-reeves-plans-canada-style-pension-funds-times-reports</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 07:01:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国经济 2022 年增长超出此前预期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/uk-economy-s-2022-growth-was-more-than-previously-estimated</link>
      <description><![CDATA[最新数据显示，英国经济在 2022 年抵御两位数通胀和政治动荡的影响比最初预想的要好，产出增长速度加快。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/uk-economy-s-2022-growth-was-more-than-previously-estimated</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 06:17:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈利法克斯称英国房价自一月份以来涨幅最大</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/uk-house-prices-rise-the-quickest-since-january-halifax-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国最大的抵押贷款机构之一表示，英国房价在三个月的低迷之后恢复增长，以自一月份以来的最快速度上涨，进一步表明市场正在应对利率上升的问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/uk-house-prices-rise-the-quickest-since-january-halifax-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 06:11:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拉贾帕克萨家族竞选总统，斯里兰卡家族回归</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/sri-lanka-party-names-rajapaksa-scion-as-presidential-candidate</link>
      <description><![CDATA[下个月，强大的拉贾帕克萨家族的一名后裔将参加斯里兰卡总统大选。两年多前，他的民粹主义叔叔领导斯里兰卡陷入了有史以来最严重的经济危机。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/sri-lanka-party-names-rajapaksa-scion-as-presidential-candidate</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 03:41:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈里斯副总裁人选沃尔兹与中国的长期关系可能会带来尴尬</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/harris-vp-pick-walz-s-long-history-with-china-may-prove-awkward</link>
      <description><![CDATA[民主党副总统候选人蒂姆·沃尔兹与中国的联系可以追溯到几十年前，这可能有助于卡玛拉·哈里斯制定应对世界第二大经济体的政策，但也可能给北京领导人和国内共和党带来麻烦。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/harris-vp-pick-walz-s-long-history-with-china-may-prove-awkward</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 00:20:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈马斯任命辛瓦尔为政治领袖，打破停火希望</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/hamas-says-leader-yahya-sinwar-will-also-become-political-chief</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哈马斯任命 10 月 7 日袭击事件的主要策划者叶海亚·辛瓦尔为其新政治领导人，这是对达成加沙停火协议的多边努力的最新打击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/hamas-says-leader-yahya-sinwar-will-also-become-political-chief</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 18:16:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非废弃市政当局欠 Eskom 45 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/south-africa-s-delinquent-municipalities-owe-eskom-4-5-billion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非各市政府共计欠 Eskom Holdings SOC Ltd. 823 亿兰特（45 亿美元）的欠款，陷入困境的这家国有电力公司正在努力收回这些欠款。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/south-africa-s-delinquent-municipalities-owe-eskom-4-5-billion</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 10:12:54 GMT</pubDate>
